title: Netherlands Foreign Direct Investment - Net Inflows
description: Foreign Direct Investment in Netherlands increased by 30626 EUR Million in the second quarter of 2022. Foreign Direct Investment in Netherlands averaged 30220.52 EUR Million from 2003 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 189388 EUR Million in the third quarter of 2007 and a record low of -248883 EUR Million in the fourth quarter of 2018. This page provides - Netherlands Foreign Direct Investment, Net Inflows - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: De Nederlandsche Bank
